verses.text_plain: Praise ye the Lord. I will praise the Lord with my whole heart, in the assembly of the upright, and in the congregation.
verses.verse_html:
1Praise ye the Lord. I will praise the Lord with my whole heart, in the assembly of the upright, and in the congregation. ▼
▼ Praise ye…: Heb. Hallelujah

footnotes.body_html: ▼ Praise ye…: Heb. Hallelujah

verses.text_plain: The works of the Lord are great, sought out of all them that have pleasure therein.
verses.verse_html: 2The works of the Lord are great, sought out of all them that have pleasure therein.

tokens.text: of all them that have pleasure

verses.text_plain: His work is honourable and glorious: and his righteousness endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 3His work is honourable and glorious: and his righteousness endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: He hath made his wonderful works to be remembered: the Lord is gracious and full of compassion.
verses.verse_html: 4He hath made his wonderful works to be remembered: the Lord is gracious and full of compassion.

verses.text_plain: He hath given meat unto them that fear him: he will ever be mindful of his covenant.
verses.verse_html:
5He hath given meat unto them that fear him: he will ever be mindful of his covenant. ▼
▼ meat: Heb. prey

verses.text_plain: He hath shewed his people the power of his works, that he may give them the heritage of the heathen.
verses.verse_html: 6He hath shewed his people the power of his works, that he may give them the heritage of the heathen.

verses.text_plain: The works of his hands are verity and judgment; all his commandments are sure.
verses.verse_html: 7The works of his hands are verity and judgment; all his commandments are sure.

verses.text_plain: They stand fast for ever and ever, and are done in truth and uprightness.
verses.verse_html:
8They stand fast for ever and ever, and are done in truth and uprightness. ▼
▼ stand…: Heb. are established

footnotes.body_html: ▼ stand…: Heb. are established

verses.text_plain: He sent redemption unto his people: he hath commanded his covenant for ever: holy and reverend is his name.
verses.verse_html: 9He sent redemption unto his people: he hath commanded his covenant for ever: holy and reverend is his name.

verses.text_plain: The fear of the Lord is the beginning of wisdom: a good understanding have all they that do his commandments: his praise endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html:
10The fear of the Lord is the beginning of wisdom: a good understanding have all they that do his commandments: his praise endureth for ever. ▼
▼ a good…: or, good success
 , ▼
▼ his commandments: Heb. them

footnotes.body_html: ▼ a good…: or, good success
▼ his commandments: Heb. them
